node.title: My second article
node.description:
Why not indeed!
I've got to find a way to escape the horrible ravages of youth. Suddenly, I'm going to the bathroom like clockwork, every three hours. And those jerks at Social Security stopped sending me checks. Now 'I'' have to pay ''them'! Hi, I'm a naughty nurse, and I really need someone to talk to. $9.95 a minute.

I'll get my kit! Switzerland is small and neutral! We are more like Germany, ambitious and misunderstood! WINDMILLS DO NOT WORK THAT WAY! GOOD NIGHT! I'll tell them you went down prying the wedding ring off his cold, dead finger.

Who am I making this out to?
Okay, it's 500 dollars, you have no choice of carrier, the battery can't hold the charge and the reception isn't veryâ€¦ Fetal stemcells, aren't those controversial? But I know you in the future. I cleaned your poop.

Yes. You gave me a dollar and some candy.
Can I use the gun?
Noooooo!
That's right, baby. I ain't your loverboy Flexo, the guy you love so much. You even love anyone pretending to be him!
You guys realize you live in a sewer, right? It may comfort you to know that Fry's death took only fifteen seconds, yet the pain was so intense, that it felt to him like fifteen years. And it goes without saying, it caused him to empty his bowels.

Would you censor the Venus de Venus just because you can see her spewers?
We'll go deliver this crate like professionals, and then we'll go home.
I just told you! You've killed me!
